import React, {Component} from "react"
import {Card, Button, Container, CardGroup, Col, Grid, Row} from "react-bootstrap";

const NewSingle = ({item}) => {
  return (
   

   
        <Col xs={12} md={4} lg={3}>
<Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>

  </Card.Body>
</Card>
</Col>




  )
   
}


export default NewSingle
